additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Intentional misuse by deliberately concentrating and inhaling contents can be harmful or fatal. Keep out of reach of children. Extremely flammable. Pressurised dispenser. Keep in a cool place away from heat and out of the sun. Avoid prolonged exposure of can to temperatures above 50C, such as may occur in cars, or near naked flame, heat or any incandescent material, for example near stoves, heaters, refrigerators. Avoid contact with food. Do not spray directly towards the eyes, face or skin. Do not puncture or incinerate this can, even when empty. Do not smoke during use.
